channel.title: Extreme lag and other problems
channel.description:
Okay, so...I'm playing around on my server. Go to sleep, get up to mess with some more stuff but when I log in...There arn't any npcs and there's a bunch of lag, wtf?
Someone Defragmented my computer recently if that's what might have done it.....
EDIT: For some characters the npcs show up...For some they do not...
